@startuml
title WebView 交互功能 - 用户主动打开前端页面并执行 JS 调用

actor 用户
participant "MainActivity" as Main
participant "WebViewActivity" as WebViewAct
participant "WebViewBridge" as Bridge
participant "WebView" as WV

用户 -> Main: 点击“打开 WebView”
Main -> WebViewAct: startActivity(Intent)
WebViewAct -> WebViewAct: onCreate()
WebViewAct -> WV: 加载 URL (本地或远程)
WV -> Bridge: 注册 JS 接口 "AndroidBridge"
用户 -> WV: 点击 HTML 按钮
WV -> Bridge: 调用 showToast()
Bridge --> WV: 弹出 Toast
WV --> 用户: 显示结果
@enduml
